<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL">&gt; Since the english voices suck shit, I have japanese voices and english text. What attack does shadow use when you fight him for the second time(at space colony ARK) that looks like Chaos Control? he isn't holding an emerald...
&gt; 
&gt; Why did Super Sonic and Hyper Shadow use Chaos Control at the end?
&gt; 
&gt; Why did Shadow die and Sonic didn't? Sonic said it was a &quot;sacrifice&quot;. For what?
&gt; 
&gt; Please help me understand...


When you fight Shadow the second time he uses Chaos Spear, which is his equal to Sonic Wind. Super Sonic and Hyper Shadow both use Chaos Control together becuase alone the don't have enough power to teleport the ARK. As for why Shadow dies and Sonic doesn't, it would end the Sonic series if they both died, and I'm sure a lot of people would find it werid if the future games were called Shadow The Hegdehog. In my mind I don't think Shadow really died. It leaves that area very vauge... Hope this clears things up. </TEXTAREA></TD>

